Just built a fully automated Club Management System using n8n! 🚀



4 workflows. 3 database tables. Zero manual work after setup.



What it does:

🔐 Member Registration — email duplicate check, bcrypt password hashing, JWT token generation, WhatsApp welcome message

📊 Member Dashboard — JWT verification + Groq AI generates a personalized membership summary

💳 Payment Processing — Razorpay webhook → 3 Supabase tables update automatically

⏰ Daily Reminder Bot — Scheduler checks expiry dates every day, sends WhatsApp reminder 3 days before expiry



Key concepts I learned building this:

• JWT authentication flow (Sign → Verify)

• Password hashing with bcrypt

• Multi-table database relations

• Webhook-driven architecture

• AI integration inside automation workflows



Tech Stack:

→ n8n (workflow automation)

→ Supabase (PostgreSQL database)

→ JWT (authentication)

→ Twilio (WhatsApp messaging)

→ Groq AI (fast AI responses)

→ Razorpay (payment gateway)



Biggest learning: Real-world systems are not just about code — it's about how data flows, how security works, and how everything connects together.



